		<h1>Dental Implants in Surrey: Permanent Solutions for Missing Teeth</h1>
		<p class="intro">
			Living with missing teeth can impact everything from your confidence to your ability to enjoy your favorite foods. Dental implants are widely considered the gold standard for tooth replacement because they look, feel, and function just like natural teeth. At our Surrey dental clinic, we specialize in advanced implant dentistry, utilizing world-renowned implant systems like <strong>Straumann BLX</strong> to restore your smile securely and permanently.
		</p>
